<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Capital Group - Case Study - Annie Sommer</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,200..800;1,6..72,200..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
   			 --primary-color: #334EAC; /* Royal */
   			 --secondary-color: #081F5C; /* Midnight */
   			 --accent-color: #7096D1; /* China */
  			--text-color: #334EAC; /* Royal for main text */
  			--text-secondary: #7096D1; /* China for secondary text */
   			 --text-muted: #BAD6EB; /* Sky for muted text */
   			 --light-gray: #F7F2EB; /* Moon */
   			 --border-color: #EDF1F6; /* Porcelain */
   			 --background-accent: #D0E3FF; /* Dawn */
            --sidebar-width: 240px; 
            --base-font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            gap: 3rem;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: var(--sidebar-width);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 2rem;
            height: fit-content;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            color: #7096D1
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: block;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        
        
        .toc {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc h3 {
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .toc li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .toc a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .toc a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color: rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.25);
            padding-left: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Active TOC link styling */
        .toc a.active {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background-color:	rgba(247, 242, 235, 0.45);
            padding-left: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        /* Smooth transition for TOC links */
        .toc a {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 3px solid transparent;
        }
        
        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 0;
            max-width: 760px;
        }
        
        .project-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .project-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .project-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .project-summary {
            font-size: .9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .content-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h3 {
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section p {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-section ul, .content-section ol {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }
        
        .content-section li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .highlight-box p, .highlight-box ul {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: var(--base-font-size);
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .image-placeholder {
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7096D1;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Thumbnail styling */
        .thumbnail {
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .thumbnail img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .thumbnail:hover img {
            filter: brightness(1.1);
        }

        /* Fullscreen modal */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1000;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal.active {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .modal-content {
            max-width: 90vw;
            max-height: 80vh;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .modal-caption {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .modal-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
        }

        .modal-close:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }
            
            .sidebar {
                width: 100%;
                position: static;
                order: 2;
            }
            
            .main-content {
                order: 1;
            }
            
            .project-header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .project-meta {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }

            /* Mobile responsive for modal */
            .modal-content {
                max-width: 95vw;
                max-height: 70vh;
            }
            
            .modal-close {
                top: 1rem;
                right: 1rem;
                width: 35px;
                height: 35px;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .modal-caption {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar with TOC -->
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back </a>
            
            <nav class="toc">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#problem">User Problem</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#strategy">Strategy</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#solution">Solution</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#insights">Insights</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="main-content">
            <header class="project-header">
                <h1>Capital Group</h1>
                
                <div class="project-meta">
                    <span><strong>Role:</strong> Senior UX/UI Designer</span>
                    <span><strong>Company:</strong><a href="https://www.capitalgroup.com/" target="_blank">Capital Group</a></span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="project-summary">
                <p>Product design for a major feature on a developer-first customer data platform</p> </div>
            </header>
            
            <section class="content-section" id="problem">
                <h2>User Problem</h2>
                <p>
                  Wholesalers at Capital Group were relying on an archaic, decade-old CRM implementation. We ported the highlights to an iPad and iOS app so users could get insights on their clients on the go
                </p>             
                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="I iterated rapidly, and talked to users as much as possible to mitigate the challenges presented by content originating in a 12 year old behemoth of a SalesForce implementation ">
                        <img src="/img/capital/capitalipad.jpg" alt="timeline for tracking plans and data catalog feature">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            
            <section class="content-section" id="strategy">
                <h2>Strategy</h2>
                <ul> 
                    <li><strong>Research:</strong>I meet with different user groups every two weeks to discuss screens in the app, future functionality, and their needs.  </li>
                    <li><strong>Define:</strong>I work in Figma to design screens to meet user needs and push the salesforce and AI-driven data to users in an elegant way </li>
                    <li><strong>Ship:</strong> I join daily standups with engineers to ship designs on a monthly release cadence </li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Low attention users</h4>
                <p>The usecase is often when users are in between meetings, on sales calls </p>
                <h4>AI in the enterprise</h4>
                <p>AI is top of mind for stakeholders and I am often tasked with bringing AI-driven insights to users </p>
               
                <h3>My Role & Contribution</h3> 
                <p>I was the sole UX/UI designer on this project. I worked most closely with a PM to ingest user needs and then would deliver based on user input.</p>
            </section> 
            
            <section class="content-section" id="solution">
                <h2>Solutions</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Users needed curated data vs volumes of data. Extracting narratives from user sessions was key to inform what charts were shown in what order.</li>
                    <li>Most users hated salesforce and didn't trust the data. Staying up to date with the latest iOS patterns and using them wherever possible drove credibility with NADIA.</li>
                    <li>Notes and unstructured data is often the most valuable in salesforce. It was important to survey what open-ended fields contained in order to design effectively.</li>
                    </ul>

                <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="I met with users to understand what narratives would be the most high-impact. I collaborated with ENG teams to learn about available AI driven analysis on ours and publicaly available data sets, in order to figure out what to visualize when.">
                        <img src="/img/capital/datavis.jpg" alt="timeline for tracking plans and data catalog feature">
                    </div>
                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="content-section" id="solution">
                <h2>Designing for finance</h2>                
             <p> Designed an iPad app on a legacy Salesforce build, working around rigid components and limited customization. The main challenge was cutting through huge amounts of institution-level data to give advisors only the information they needed, in a clear and touch-friendly format.</p>
               <!-- <div class="image-placeholder">
                    <div class="thumbnail" data-caption="We kept explorations of more iOS-standard redesigns because we knew a redesign was needed eventually.">
                        <img src="/img/capital/capitalredesign.jpg" alt="capital group redesign">          
                    </div>
                </div> -->

            
            </section>
            <section class="content-section" id="insights">
                <h2>Insights</h2>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Enterprise data distrust</h3>
                    <p>Users had fluid levels of trust among data sets and data points, depending on the source, the type of data, etc. This was crucial to understand for successful designs and meant designing with faux data wouldn't work. A lot of time was spent surveying data quality.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Internal users resist change</h3>
                    <p>I am now an expert at working with internal users, having done it at mulitple companies, and they are always resistant to change. Navigating this as a designer means bringing them into the process as early as possible rather than backloading that effort into selilng solutions created in isolation.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>AI in the enterprise</h3>
                    <p>Small, nimble teams with custom solutions within massive enterprises can drive massive amounts of productivity. Both Ford and Capital groups ran similar models, of teams structured like micro-startups within the company hunting for AI use cases. I find it to be a good approach.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            
